name: egison
description: Egison is a purely functional programming language with non-linear pattern-matching against non-free data types. We can directly pattern-match against a wide range of data types such as lists, multisets, sets, trees and graphs with Egison.

name: api.egison.org
description: The API server for Egison's website

name: egison-ruby
description: A Ruby gem for non-linear pattern-matching with backtracking

name: egison-scheme
description: Scheme macros for non-linear pattern matching with backtracking for non-free data types

name: egison-haskell
description: Template Haskell Implementation of Egison Pattern Matching
